@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nPOST /api/invoices/purchase" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Wallet" as WalletDB
participant "Database\nTable: WalletTx" as WalletTxDB
participant "Database\nTable: Transaction" as TxDB
participant "Database\nTable: Invoice" as InvoiceDB
participant "Database\nTable: Receipt" as ReceiptDB
participant "Database\nTable: EnergyOffer" as OfferDB
participant "Database\nTable: MeterInfo" as MeterDB
participant "Ethereum/Hardhat" as Chain
User->UI: Select an offer to purchase energy
UI->API: Submit energy purchase request
API->WalletDB: Validate buyer balance and update buyer/seller wallets
WalletDB-->API: Wallet balances updated
API->WalletTxDB: Store wallet movement records
WalletTxDB-->API: Wallet transaction records stored
API->TxDB: Store buyer/seller transaction records
TxDB-->API: Transaction records stored
API->InvoiceDB: Create invoice record
InvoiceDB-->API: Invoice created
API->ReceiptDB: Create receipt record
ReceiptDB-->API: Receipt created
API->OfferDB: Update purchased offer status
OfferDB-->API: Offer updated
API->MeterDB: Update battery or meter state if required
MeterDB-->API: Meter data updated
API->Chain: Publish buyer/seller transaction proof
Chain-->API: Return txHash and block metadata
API->TxDB: Update transaction verification
TxDB-->API: Verification updated
API-->UI: Return purchase result
UI-->User: Display purchase result and related transactions

@enduml
